{% extends "base.jinja" %}
{% block title %}Contributing{% endblock %}
{% block content %}

<h1>Contributing</h1>

<p>Amphib is built on Hiring Agent — and we keep building. Contributions welcome.</p>

<h2>Bugs</h2>

<p>Open an issue. Include: description, environment (OS, Python version, commit), steps to reproduce, and logs.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>

<p>Check existing requests first, then open a new one with the problem and your proposed solution.</p>

<h2>Code</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Open an issue to discuss the change.</li>
  <li>Fork, branch, code.</li>
  <li>Format with <a href="https://black.readthedocs.io/en/stable/">Black</a>.</li>
  <li>Keep prompts provider-agnostic.</li>
  <li>Test with a real resume on Ollama (and Gemini if you have a key).</li>
  <li>Open a PR.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Commit style</h2>

<pre><code>fix: handle en dash date ranges in work parser
feat: add configurable scoring weights</code></pre>

<p>Reference the issue number when applicable.</p>

<h2>Conduct</h2>

<p>Be respectful. Report issues to the maintainers.</p>

{% endblock %}
